    "A limitation of our study, and a potential source of sampling bias, is that only a relatively small number of participants from a single medical center were recruited",
    "Clinicians are generally supportive of the use of LLMs for many tasks in clinical practice, research, and education, especially where LLMs play a supportive role to humans.",
